# License Notice for views/src/

This directory contains files under two different licenses:

## Mozilla Public License 2.0 (MPL 2.0)

The following files are derived from the original Firefox Send project
(by Mozilla Corporation) and the community fork by timvisee, and are
licensed under the Mozilla Public License Version 2.0:

- api.mjs
- archive.mjs
- ece.mjs
- fileReceiver.mjs
- fileSender.mjs
- keychain.mjs
- ownedFile.mjs
- streams.mjs
- zip.mjs

These files contain the core cryptographic and file transfer logic from
the original Firefox Send implementation and have been preserved with
minimal modifications (primarily converting from CommonJS to ES Modules).

The full text of the Mozilla Public License 2.0 can be found at:
https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/MPL/2.0/

## GNU General Public License v3.0 (GPL-3.0)

All other files in this directory and subdirectories are licensed under
the GNU General Public License version 3.0.

This includes but is not limited to:
- All UI components in ui/
- Application initialization and routing (main.mjs)
- Controller and state management (controller.mjs)
- Utility functions not derived from Firefox Send
- All new features and implementations

The full text of the GNU General Public License v3.0 can be found at:
https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.html

